#define WrestleWin ["JARVIS, remind me to check my system diagnostics. That wasn't even a workout. Try harder next time, %s.","Was that a fight, or were you just trying to get my autograph, %s? Either way, you're done.","My suit's power levels are still at 99%. Don't call me when you have a real challenge, %s.","I’ve seen toaster ovens with more structural integrity. Go home, %s.","That was almost cute. Almost. Beat it, kid, I'm busy.","You're cute, %s, but you're operating with obsolete technology. Upgrade or stay out of my way.","Data analysis complete: You have a 0% chance of winning. Should’ve checked the stats, %s.","Did you really think you could take down the Iron Avenger with that? Hilarious.","I'm not even using the repulsors at full capacity. Don't take it personally, %s.","You're a nuisance, %s. Go find a sandbox to play in.","Not bad, %s. You're actually starting to register on my tactical display.","You forced me to expend some energy. I'll give you credit for that, at least, %s.","Better than the average grunt, but nowhere near my league. Nice try, though.","You've got some potential, %s. Try not to waste it on losing fights.","I'm impressed you're still standing—barely. Time to call it a day, %s.","Welcome to the big leagues, %s. You're actually making me sweat a little.","I see what you were trying to do there, %s. A decent strategy, but I'm faster.","That was a solid engagement, %s. My armor will need a polish, but it was worth it.","You're holding your own, %s. Don't let it go to your head, though.","You're a decent combatant, %s. If you ever want to upgrade, look me up.","Whoa! %s, you're actually putting up a fight! This is getting interesting.","You've got some real firepower, %s! Let’s see if you can take this.","You pushed me, %s. That’s more than most can say. Don't feel too bad about losing.","You're a powerhouse, %s. I might have to start taking you seriously.","I'm genuinely enjoying this, %s. Don't make me finish it just yet!","Okay, %s, you've officially earned my attention. Impressive display.","You're strong, %s. And you've got good taste in gear. But still—my win.","I’ve been looking for a real sparring partner. You’re definitely top-tier, %s.","That was a high-intensity engagement, %s. My systems are actually liking this.","You're every bit as good as your reputation, %s. Glad I brought the heavy armor.","Holy atoms! You're off the charts, %s! Welcome to the big show—and the losing side today.","Finally! Someone capable of making me use 100% capacity. This was a match for the ages, %s.","You're a legend, %s. If you weren't such a headache, I'd invite you to the Avengers.","With your strength and my tech, we could run this city. Too bad you're on the wrong side, %s.","You're truly elite, %s. I'm honored to have been the one to take you down."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["JARVIS, check the sensors! Something's malfunctioning—I clearly didn't just lose to that.","Okay, that was a glitch! A massive, unexpected glitch. I'm blaming the software, %s.","Lucky shot, %s. Don't get used to it. I'm going back to the lab to fix this.","That wasn't a defeat, that was a... strategic retreat. Yeah, that's it.","You caught me off guard, %s. Don't expect it to happen again!","You're full of surprises, %s. I need to recalibrate my tactics.","I'm not used to this... feeling. I don't like it. But fair play, I suppose.","I guess I underestimated you, %s. Point taken. Literally.","You got a lucky hit in, %s. Enjoy the moment.","We're done here. I have a suit to repair.","You're holding your own, %s! Guess you're better than I thought.","You actually caught me. I'm... confused. Good win, %s.","You've got potential, %s. Don't let it go to your head, but that was a solid play.","Nice move, %s! I'm going to have to study that one.","My sensors were off, %s. But you definitely took advantage of it.","Welcome to the winners' circle, %s. Hope you're ready for the rematch!","Everything heating up too fast for me today? Seems so, %s!","You’re handling yourself pretty well, %s. That’s a nice change of pace.","Keep it up, %s! I like someone who can actually keep pace with me.","Looks like you’re ready for some real action, %s. Let’s get to it next time!","Whoa! %s, you’re on fire today! You really showed me!","You’ve got some real skill, %s. I like it! You definitely earned that win.","Now that’s what I’m talking about, %s! You’re really heating things up.","I’m impressed, %s. Honestly, you're playing at a whole new level.","You’re doing great, %s! Keep showing 'em how it’s done!","Hey, %s! You want to race? You clearly know how to handle yourself!","I’ve seen some heavy hitters, but you’re right up there, %s. You really got me!","You’re dangerous, %s. I like that! Makes for a much better fight.","Finally, a challenge! You didn't hold back at all, %s!","You’ve got moves to spare, %s! Any chance you can help me with the suit repair?","Holy smokes! %s, you’re basically a living supercomputer! You burned right through my defenses!","I thought I was the tech expert around here! Looks like I’ve got serious competition, %s.","You’re a total legend, %s. Let’s team up and give this place a real show!","Finally, someone who can handle the heat! You win this one, %s!","If I wasn't so modest, %s, I’d say you were almost as cool as me. But today, you're the winner!"]
